      • popStep

        public ShowcaseContext.Step popStep()
        Pops previous step from history setting it as a current step.

        It will remove params if context has state COMPLETED and the state will be reset to HAS_NEXT_STEP.

        If history is empty nothing will be done.

        Returns:
        previous step
